### 2. Component Dependency Declaration Patterns

Components declare dependencies in two ways:

**In registry entries** (from `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775473867919-51afi3/apps/v4/registry/bases/base/ui/_registry.ts`):

